    "description": "<strong>官方Q群：513889336</strong><br><br><strong>这是一款操作时间轴，规划路线的益智解谜游戏，据说能通关的人IQ都在180以上。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍</h2><br>在游戏中，玩家需要让场景中的小球沿着格子移动顺利到达终点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/c40396e0f72b5d6f2569c61a0da68f89.poster.avif?t=1753173946\" width=604 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/c40396e0f72b5d6f2569c61a0da68f89.webm?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/c40396e0f72b5d6f2569c61a0da68f89.mp4?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>小球拥有自己的“时间轴”，时间轴包含“上”、“下”、“左”、“右”以及“不动”这五种行动指令，玩家可以任意排列行动指令的顺序，由此改变时间轴的运行，让球到达终点。有些关卡，玩家需要操纵的球会变为两个，两球相撞会产生额外的位移，由此带来更加灵活多样的移动策略。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/d4e4429714888db6b1c8684983370623.poster.avif?t=1753173946\" width=604 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/d4e4429714888db6b1c8684983370623.webm?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/d4e4429714888db6b1c8684983370623.mp4?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中还加入了“传送带”机制，传送带本身也有自己的时间轴，如何合理规划它的行动顺序也是需要仔细考虑的一点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/606045c284d6fca0d45f7518665c4d00.poster.avif?t=1753173946\" width=604 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/606045c284d6fca0d45f7518665c4d00.webm?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/606045c284d6fca0d45f7518665c4d00.mp4?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >怎么样，是不是很简单，学会了吗？<br>那么剩下的200+有趣多样的关卡，就交给你了！~</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/1bcb8cc34b695032d3091cf79e08523f.poster.avif?t=1753173946\" width=604 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/1bcb8cc34b695032d3091cf79e08523f.webm?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861120/extras/1bcb8cc34b695032d3091cf79e08523f.mp4?t=1753173946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
